1
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,260
♪Wandering alone♪

2
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,540
♪Walking far by dusk-lit streets♪

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:27,430
♪Your eyes are as cold as clouds♪

4
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,970
♪Faintly coming into view♪

5
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:30,360
♪The city lights♪

6
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,630
♪Lit up that single moment♪

7
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:36,140
♪I can't hide or stop missing you♪

8
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,640
♪I can't forget those moments♪

9
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
♪Losing you♪

10
00:00:39,610 --> 00:00:41,320
♪Like the seasons in my memory♪

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,290
♪Without winter♪

12
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,920
♪Walking down the long, dark street♪

13
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,460
♪Snow will never fall again♪

14
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,200
♪Our old story was torn♪

15
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,610
♪Into scattered pieces♪

16
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,430
♪Replaying every single scene♪

17
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,980
♪After you left♪

18
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,510
♪As if our documentary♪

19
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:03,120
♪Lost winter♪

20
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,180
♪The breeze speaks of good times♪

21
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,080
♪Pure white devotion♪

22
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,990
♪Send out a letter♪

23
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:17,780
♪Carrying my longing♪

24
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:20,980
=The Double Game=

25
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 11=

26
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,320
(Email)
Lin Zhi'er,

27
00:01:25,350 --> 00:01:26,280
Lin Youqiang has died.

28
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:27,660
Come back for the funeral.

29
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,120
Did I scare you?

30
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:41,960
I was worried,

31
00:01:41,971 --> 00:01:43,011
so I came to check on you.

32
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:46,920
He was raising hell by day,

33
00:01:47,870 --> 00:01:49,120
and by night, he was gone.

34
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,480
Life really is unpredictable.

35
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:55,880
Yeah.

36
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:58,350
Death falls

37
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,680
all of a sudden.

38
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,710
I wonder what Lin Zhi'er is thinking

39
00:02:05,310 --> 00:02:06,200
and if she'll be back.

40
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,150
The news blew up today.

41
00:02:08,310 --> 00:02:09,400
She must already know.

42
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:10,680
She knows

43
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:11,960
what to do.

44
00:02:12,470 --> 00:02:13,520
You didn't hear it.

45
00:02:13,870 --> 00:02:15,590
Lu Jianchuan was just trying to use her

46
00:02:15,710 --> 00:02:16,750
to take Linhai Group.

47
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,710
This isn't his first time.

48
00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:23,550
I think

49
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,520
Lin Zhi'er will come back.

50
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,800
If I were her,

51
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:30,590
even with a father like Lin Youqiang,

52
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:34,470
I'd still come back for his funeral.

53
00:02:36,590 --> 00:02:37,430
Alright.

54
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,520
Don't overthink it.

55
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:39,960
Get some rest.

56
00:02:46,150 --> 00:02:46,990
Good night.

57
00:03:13,910 --> 00:03:15,280
Your parents don't want you.

58
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:17,750
You're just a stray kid.

59
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,680
You'll spend

60
00:03:18,710 --> 00:03:19,870
your whole life alone.

61
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:20,960
- Brat!
- Brat!

62
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:21,960
No one wants you.

63
00:03:24,030 --> 00:03:25,370
- A stray kid!
- Exactly.

64
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,240
A stray kid.

65
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:27,800
Exactly.

66
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:28,680
A little brat!

67
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,080
Lin Zhi'er,

68
00:03:42,150 --> 00:03:43,030
I knew you'd come.

69
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:49,150
I'm here to see him off.

70
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,430
I always knew this day would come.

71
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,430
I just didn't expect it so soon.

72
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:58,920
My condolences.

73
00:04:00,470 --> 00:04:01,400
Let's switch back.

74
00:04:02,190 --> 00:04:04,030
Linhai Group is waiting for you.

75
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,520
No.

76
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,520
I don't want ties with him anymore.

77
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,710
You take over for me.

78
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,310
Are you kidding me?

79
00:04:15,190 --> 00:04:17,000
We do look alike,

80
00:04:17,270 --> 00:04:19,000
but I'm nothing to Lin Youqiang.

81
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:19,960
- No.
- I...

82
00:04:20,270 --> 00:04:21,110
Wen Yan,

83
00:04:22,390 --> 00:04:23,310
you're not nothing

84
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:25,510
to Lin Youqiang.

85
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:27,830
You're his daughter too.

86
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:37,960
What did you say?

87
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,090
I once asked you

88
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,310
if we were real sisters.

89
00:04:58,680 --> 00:04:59,680
You said we weren't.

90
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:01,350
That's right.

91
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,480
I lied to you last time.

92
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:05,870
If you'd learned the truth,

93
00:05:06,630 --> 00:05:07,763
you might go to Lin Youqiang,

94
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,830
and he'd use you and hurt you.

95
00:05:15,430 --> 00:05:16,480
The first time we met,

96
00:05:18,270 --> 00:05:19,600
it felt unbelievable to me.

97
00:05:20,750 --> 00:05:23,040
So, I checked the clinic
on Lianxin Island.

98
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,400
Our mother

99
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,070
gave birth to twins.

100
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:29,600
That means you

101
00:05:30,630 --> 00:05:31,470
and me.

102
00:05:43,630 --> 00:05:45,070
We really are sisters.

103
00:05:50,190 --> 00:05:51,030
I knew it.

104
00:05:51,390 --> 00:05:52,270
How could there be

105
00:05:52,430 --> 00:05:54,070
two people who look identical?

106
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:01,800
What about our mom?

107
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,640
I don't know either.

108
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:07,950
She may have died long ago.

109
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,870
Otherwise, how could a mother

110
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,040
ignore her daughters

111
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:16,070
for over 20 years?

112
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,840
That's strange.

113
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:21,190
We're twins.

114
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,390
Why did Lin Youqiang only take you,

115
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,270
leaving me in the orphanage?

116
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,760
I have no idea.

117
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,800
But Lin Youqiang seems unaware of you.

118
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,400
It's hard to say

119
00:06:34,070 --> 00:06:36,630
which one of us had it worse.

120
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:39,720
If you want to learn about your past,

121
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,160
please stay.

122
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,310
I need your help.

123
00:06:47,830 --> 00:06:49,720
But inheriting all this so suddenly...

124
00:06:49,870 --> 00:06:51,310
You're Lin Youqiang's daughter too.

125
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:54,270
You have every right to inherit it.

126
00:06:58,950 --> 00:07:00,160
Don't you want to find out

127
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,600
the truth about Lianxin Island?

128
00:07:04,510 --> 00:07:06,120
As the CEO of Linhai Group,

129
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,870
you'll be one step closer to it.

130
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,880
Okay.

131
00:07:20,310 --> 00:07:21,150
I'll stay

132
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,920
and keep Linhai Group for you.

133
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,310
I'll get to the truth for sure.

134
00:07:27,750 --> 00:07:29,040
I believe our mother

135
00:07:29,830 --> 00:07:31,630
wouldn't leave us for no reason.

136
00:07:40,510 --> 00:07:41,350
They're here.

137
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:44,350
I should go now.

138
00:07:44,390 --> 00:07:45,230
Take care.

139
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,400
Sis,

140
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:52,270
take care of yourself.

141
00:08:11,020 --> 00:08:13,020
(Mr. Lin Youqiang)

142
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,200
Everyone,

143
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,560
based on the estate notarization,

144
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:28,040
Chairman Lin's assets included

145
00:08:28,430 --> 00:08:30,430
16 properties of various kinds,

146
00:08:31,630 --> 00:08:33,910
1,080 collectible items,

147
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:36,550
48 million in cash,

148
00:08:36,870 --> 00:08:38,320
and shares in listed companies,

149
00:08:38,539 --> 00:08:39,732
which are valued on the market

150
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:41,200
at around 800 million in total,

151
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,000
as well as a 43% stake

152
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,600
in Linhai Group.

153
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:46,910
Since Chairman Lin left no will,

154
00:08:47,550 --> 00:08:48,390
under the law,

155
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,150
his only daughter, Lin Zhi'er,

156
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,440
is the first-priority heir.

157
00:08:51,790 --> 00:08:54,030
She will inherit all his assets.

158
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,480
Now, Youqiang is gone,

159
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,360
leaving behind a huge estate.

160
00:09:01,510 --> 00:09:02,510
It's not easy to handle.

161
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:04,510
We all understand what the lawyer said

162
00:09:04,577 --> 00:09:05,663
about the succession order.

163
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,320
But

164
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:09,120
letting Zhi'er inherit it all alone

165
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,280
is a little...

166
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,170
Exactly.

167
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,320
When your dad was alive,

168
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:14,480
we helped your family

169
00:09:14,630 --> 00:09:16,720
and the Group a lot.

170
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:18,473
Even if not credited,
we gave our effort.

171
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:19,910
The law is the law,

172
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,080
but we have feelings.

173
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,480
As for dividing the property,

174
00:09:23,910 --> 00:09:25,240
could you think it over again?

175
00:09:26,630 --> 00:09:27,720
Yeah, Zhi'er.

176
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,320
We're family, after all.

177
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:32,200
You can't let those of us
who spent years

178
00:09:32,510 --> 00:09:33,790
working for the Lin family

179
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:34,790
end up hurt, right?

180
00:09:35,390 --> 00:09:36,840
Try giving us a share.

181
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:39,120
Let us help carry some of it too.

182
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,200
- Exactly.
- Right.

183
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,750
Thanks for your concern, everyone.

184
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:45,150
You've really worried so much for me.

185
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,750
You keep calling yourselves family.

186
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:52,440
When I was ignored in the family,

187
00:09:53,150 --> 00:09:53,990
where were you?

188
00:09:55,630 --> 00:09:57,080
When I was forced to marry,

189
00:09:57,870 --> 00:09:59,440
and my dignity was trampled on,

190
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:00,960
where were you then?

191
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:03,470
Zhi'er,

192
00:10:03,750 --> 00:10:05,670
we're talking to you nicely here.

193
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,840
Your words

194
00:10:07,270 --> 00:10:08,360
really hurt our feelings.

195
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:11,000
We never meant to take your inheritance.

196
00:10:11,390 --> 00:10:13,030
We just want you to share a little.

197
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,320
Is that wrong?

198
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:15,440
Nicely?

199
00:10:16,870 --> 00:10:18,720
My dad has just died,

200
00:10:19,030 --> 00:10:21,200
and you're already here for the estate.

201
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,480
Treating an orphan like this,

202
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:25,720
aren't you afraid of karma?

203
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:26,920
You...

204
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:29,120
Zhi'er, how can you say that?

205
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,630
That's exactly how I talk.

206
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,670
(In Memory)
My succession is lawful.

207
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,480
If you have any objections,

208
00:10:35,390 --> 00:10:36,510
go and sue me.

209
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,280
No, she...

210
00:10:39,670 --> 00:10:41,840
You won't share even a little?

211
00:10:42,030 --> 00:10:43,083
That's too cold.

212
00:10:43,094 --> 00:10:44,471
- Ridiculous.
- You can't do this.

213
00:10:44,482 --> 00:10:45,589
- Exactly.
- How absurd.

214
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,670
- Calm down.
- Right.

215
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:01,470
Tingxiao.

216
00:11:17,540 --> 00:11:18,990
♪This door♪

217
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:24,140
♪Lets in the sky outside♪

218
00:11:24,620 --> 00:11:28,180
♪With a voice even lighter♪

219
00:11:28,180 --> 00:11:30,990
♪Than how you just greeted me♪

220
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,810
♪I know now♪

221
00:11:33,140 --> 00:11:38,020
♪What the chill in my body means♪

222
00:11:38,370 --> 00:11:41,240
♪The moment salt hits the wound♪

223
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:44,860
♪My heart still beats so naively♪

224
00:11:45,030 --> 00:11:48,020
♪To complete♪

225
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:52,230
♪A joy that needs no brave pretense♪

226
00:11:52,370 --> 00:11:54,870
♪How cruel sincerity can be♪

227
00:11:55,010 --> 00:11:58,560
♪Like a door with no key♪

228
00:11:58,870 --> 00:12:01,190
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

229
00:12:01,190 --> 00:12:04,770
♪The tears in my eyes♪

230
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:08,030
♪You looked like you had nothing to say♪

231
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:09,770
♪Then got so good at being cold♪

232
00:12:09,770 --> 00:12:12,610
♪That's why a smile feels so precious♪

233
00:12:12,820 --> 00:12:14,910
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

234
00:12:15,060 --> 00:12:19,390
♪The tears burned into my heart♪

235
00:12:19,770 --> 00:12:22,060
♪Let's say silence was just for show♪

236
00:12:22,060 --> 00:12:26,730
♪Even if I've grown another year♪
